{
  "_doc": [
    "v6 multi-account credential file. Copy to accounts.json and fill in.",
    "Order matters — accounts are tried in order.",
    "On 1095 / quota / sign-in failure, the rotator advances to the next account in the list.",
    "State is tracked in .cca/active_accounts.json (auto-created).",
    "accounts.json is gitignored — never commit real credentials."
  ],

